metadata.name: Serious Schnauzers #1
metadata.description:
Serious Schnauzers is a nft project based off of one of the most unique and lovable dog breeds ever.

My family has owned many schnauzers over the years and they have all had incredible personalities but they only shared one trait they loved us as a family unconditionally. I hope this nft collection will bring back as many happy memories for you as it did for me.
